        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Distribution of Rhamnus nigricans, Sageretia cordiformis, S. ellipsoidea, and S. lucida. The sites were obtained from the specimen records, our field investigations and photo information in CFH and PPBC." , "Figure 4. Field photos of Sageretia cordiformis (A, B) and S. thea (C, D) A and C habit B and D fruiting branch and leaf blades A-C photographed by Y. Yang, D by X. X. Zhu." , "Figure 3. Type specimens of Sageretia cordifolia, S. cordiformis and S. thea A, B isotypes of S. cordifolia (A: P [P 01818867]; B: P [06765093]) C holotype of S. cordiformis (KUN [1207932]) D isotype of S. cordiformis (KUN [1207933]) E, F isotypes of S. thea (E: S [S 11 - 12914]; F: LD [1749752]). A, B and E, F obtained from GBIF, C, D from NOI (https: // noi. link /)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/556308" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/556310" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/556309" .

